    <p>Objectives</p>
    <p>History  Access Matrix (Lampson 1969)</p>
    <p>Rule-Based Access Control (LaPadula 1973)</p>
    <p>Discretionary Access Control (DAC) and Mandatory Access Control (MAC) (DoD, 1973)</p>
    <p>Role-based Access Control (Sandhu 1996)</p>
    <p>Attribute-based Access Control (Chen 2011)</p>
    <p>Temporal Role-based Access Control model (Bertino 2001)</p>
    <p>And many others (Motta 2003; Ni 2010; etc.)</p>
  </div>
  <div class="page">
    <p>Objectives (2)</p>
    <p>Limitations of existing work Few of these works have addressed</p>
    <p>information access management in the context of team collaboration and workflow</p>
