  <div class="page">
    <p>Discussion</p>
    <p>First application of access control model for clinical education programs</p>
    <p>Access control is not just restriction of access permissions</p>
    <p>Limitation</p>
    <p>Error analysis  Mistakes in preparing invitation data for the study cases to</p>
    <p>feed EnhancedRBAC</p>
    <p>Situation to add/delete data directly to/from the CEI Admin database</p>
    <p>Fault in querying workflow status of the study cases from CEI Admin System</p>
  </div>
  <div class="page">
    <p>Conclusion</p>
    <p>Successfully developed a system framework to implement the EnhancedRBAC model</p>
    <p>Initial evaluation has shown that this system framework can be effectively used for clinical education</p>
    <p>Future work  Extension of this system framework to support the continues</p>
    <p>development of EnhancedRBAC</p>
    <p>Deployment of the framework to other domain applications for clinical education, biomedical research, and patient care</p>
